pendent (politician)/meta/color}}| \n| Citizens\n|-\n| align=center|{{sort|26|26}} \n| align=center|{{sort|21|21}} \n| [[Joseph Medill]]\n| 1871\n| 1873\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2\n| bgcolor={{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}}| \n| [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] ([[Prohibitionism|Dry]])\n|-\n| \n|\n| [[Lester L. Bond]]<br>(acting)\n| 1873\n| 1873\n| align=center| {{sort|.25|{{frac|1|4}}}}\n| align=center| {{sort|.5|{{frac|1|2}}}}\n| bgcolor={{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}}| \n| [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|-\n| align=center|{{sort|27|27}} \n| align=center|{{sort|22|22}} \n| [[Harvey Doolittle Colvin]]\n| 1873\n| 1875\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2\n| bgcolor={{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}}| \n| [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] ([[Prohibitionism|Wet]])\n|-\n| align=center|{{sort|28|28}} \n| align=center|{{sort|23|23}} \n| [[Monroe Heath]]\n| 1876\n| 1879\n| align=center| 2 \n| align=center| 4\n| bgcolor={{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}}| \n| [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|-\n| align=center|{{sort|29|29}} \n| align=center|{{sort|24|24}} \n| [[Carter Harrison Sr.]] \n| 1879\n| 1887\n| align=center| 4\n| align=center| 8\n| bgcolor={{Democratic Party (United States)/meta/color}}| \n| [[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|-\n| align=center|{{sort|30|30}} \n| align=center|{{sort|25|25}} \n| [[John A. Roche]]\n| 1887\n| 1889\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2\n| bgcolor={{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}}| \n| [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|-\n| align=center|{{sort|31|31}} \n| align=center|{{sort|26|26}} \n| [[DeWitt C. Cregier]] \n| 1889\n| 1891\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2\n| bgcolor={{Democratic Party (United States)/meta/color}}| \n| [[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|-\n| align=center|{{sort|32|32}} \n| align=center|{{sort|27|27}} \n| [[Hempstead Washburne